{{Quote|The Duloks paid top rate to have me take it off their hands. No, it was the Dragon Riders of Poolok!|The Gonster arguing with himself over the origin of the Hoosha|<ref name="The Raich">{{Ewoks|The Raich}}</ref>}}
The '''Dragon Riders of Poolok''' was an organization that was apparently known for using [[dragon]]s as mounts. They had once come into contact with [[Gonster]] who was known for his skill in dealing with monstrous beasts. The Dragon Riders had apparently appealed to the Gonster to help rid them of a terrifying beast known as the [[Hoosha]]. However, the Gonster could not agree over whether that particular monster had been related with the Dragon Riders or with the [[Dulok/Legends|Duloks]], so it's possible that the Gonster had aided the Dragon Riders with a completely unrelated beast.

